{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ef82ee8437","title":"关于中央各部委干部参加劳动的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c6b7a5d8c2","index":0,"year":1958,"month":6,"day":15,"articleId":"ef82ee8437"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji39","name":"毛泽东全集第39卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/39-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji39":{"comments":[{"id":"0cbd30ebbc","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"ef82ee8437","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在农垦部部长王震1958年6月13日给毛泽东、中央的报告上。报告说：“农垦部三分之二的干部已于五月底分赴密山、佳木斯等基区参加劳动，一律下场四个月，进行现场整风，学习八大二次会议文件和帮助农场工作。我个人拟待十七日处理完下放任务后，也去密山、佳木斯基区。”"},{"id":"30dc4d3387","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"ef82ee8437","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"小平，即邓小平，当时任中共中央总书记、国务院副总理。"}],"contents":[{"id":"c707a70776","type":"title","text":"关于中央各部委干部参加劳动的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"ef82ee8437"},{"id":"0cbd30ebbc","type":"paragraph","text":"小平c同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"ef82ee8437"},{"id":"30dc4d3387","type":"paragraph","text":"这好像是一个彻底的办法。请你想一下，并和一些同志谈一下，有些党、政、军部委，或者多数部委，都仿农垦部做法，是否可以呢？三分之二下去，三分之一留家，下去四个月，似乎可以吧？究竟如何？请你的定。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"ef82ee8437"},{"id":"b0d9c955bd","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"ef82ee8437"},{"id":"735b00a4e2","type":"paragraph","text":"六月十五日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"ef82ee8437"}],"page":{"id":"9e11334624","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"ef82ee8437","start":402,"end":402}}}},"__N_SSG":true}